[[米罗斯拉夫·克洛泽|米罗斯拉夫·克洛泽]]是[[德国国家足球队|德国国家足球队]]史上最佳射手，2001至2014年共参赛137场并射入71球<ref>{{cite web | title = (West) Germany – Record International Players | archivedate = 2020-06-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200617090526/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/duit-recintlp.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/duit-recintlp.html | publisher = [[RSSSF|Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation]] | accessdate = 2020-07-24}}</ref>。他同时也是[[国际足协世界杯|国际足协世界杯]]的世界最佳射手，从[[2002年国际足协世界杯|2002]]至[[2014年国际足协世界杯|2014年]]共参加四届国际足协世界杯的24场比赛，前后16次把球送进对手大门<ref name="sixteen">{{cite news | title = World Cup 2014: Miroslav Klose breaks finals goals record | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/28169062 | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | publisher = BBC Sport | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190322223658/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/28169062 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2019-03-22 | date = 2014-07-08}}</ref>。克洛泽为德国队效力的13年间，所有比赛只要他得过分，球队就从没输过比赛<ref name="sixteen" />。

2001年3月24日，克洛泽在[[2002年國際足協世界盃外圍賽#歐洲/亞洲|2002年国际足协世界杯资格赛]]首次随德国队走上国际赛场并攻破[[阿尔巴尼亚国家足球队|阿尔巴尼亚队]]大门，帮助球队以2比1取胜。2002年2月13日，他在[[凯撒斯劳滕|凯撒斯劳滕]][[弗里茨·瓦尔特体育场|弗里茨·瓦尔特体育场]]首度达成国际赛事[[帽子戏法|帽子戏法]]，球队最终以7比1轻取[[以色列国家男子足球队|以色列队]]<ref name="israel">{{cite news | last = Bright | first1 = Richard | title = International round-up: Klose hat-trick as Germans thrash Israel | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2002-02-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160229025301/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/2430745/International-round-up-Klose-hat-trick-as-Germans-thrash-Israel.html | archivedate = 2016-02-29 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/2430745/International-round-up-Klose-hat-trick-as-Germans-thrash-Israel.html | accessdate = 2020-07-25}}</ref>，接下来他又于5月18日故伎重演，德国队又以6比2大胜[[奥地利国家足球队|奥地利队]]<ref name="austria">{{cite news | title = Deisler injured in German win | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181107010907/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/germany/newsid_1995000/1995975.stm | archivedate = 2018-11-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/germany/newsid_1995000/1995975.stm | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2002-05-18}}</ref>。打入世界杯后，他共计踢入五球，与[[巴西国家足球队|巴西队]]的[[里瓦尔多|里瓦尔多]]并列第二，仅次于[[罗纳尔多|罗纳尔多]]。克洛泽在2002年世界杯的进球全部来自小组赛，首先是在[[札幌巨蛋|札幌巨蛋]]向[[沙特阿拉伯国家男子足球队|沙特阿拉伯队]]表演帽子戏法，帮助球队以8比0大败对手<ref name="saudi">{{cite news | title = Germany savage Saudis | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2002-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200627161647/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/matches_wallchart/germany_v_saudi_arabia/default.stm | archivedate = 2020-06-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/matches_wallchart/germany_v_saudi_arabia/default.stm}}</ref>。

克洛泽在[[2006年国际足协世界杯|2006年国际足协世界杯]]的[[2006年世界杯足球赛决赛周_-_A组|开场比赛]]就两次攻破[[哥斯达黎加国家足球队|哥斯达黎加队]]大门，德国队以4比2取胜<ref name="crica">{{cite news | title = Germany 4–2 Costa Rica | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4852498.stm | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2006-06-09 | archive-date = 2017-12-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171224223305/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4852498.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，接下来他又在最后一场小组赛对[[厄瓜多尔国家足球队|厄瓜多尔队]]梅开二度，德国队以3比0轻松胜出<ref name="ecuador">{{cite news | title = Ecuador 0–3 Germany | archivedate = 2020-01-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200121100719/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853270.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853270.stm | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | publisher = BBC Sport | deadurl = no | date = 2006-06-20}}</ref>。此次世界杯他又踢入五球，获[[世界杯金靴奖|世界杯金靴奖]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Sent-off Zidane named best player | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/5154248.stm | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2006-07-10 | archive-date = 2012-05-21 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/67p7wW9OW?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/5154248.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2008年9月10日，克洛泽在[[2010年国际足协世界杯外围赛|2010年国际足协世界杯资格赛]]对阵[[芬兰国家足球队|芬兰队]]的比赛中第四次表演国际帽子戏法，为德国队最终以3比3追平立下汗马功劳<ref name="finland">{{cite news | title = Klose Scores Hat-trick as Germany Rescue Point in Finland | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | publisher = [[德国之声|Deutsche Welle]] | date = 2008-09-11 | url = http://www.dw.com/en/klose-scores-hat-trick-as-germany-rescue-point-in-finland/a-3635824 | archivedate = 2019-04-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190418201156/https://www.dw.com/en/klose-scores-hat-trick-as-germany-rescue-point-in-finland/a-3635824}}</ref>。打入[[2010年国际足协世界杯|正式比赛]]后，他在南非赛场共攻进四球，其中包括他[[国际赛事出场100次以上的男子足球运动员列表|第100次出场]]的四分之一决赛两次攻破阿根廷球门，协助球队以4比0大胜<ref name="argentina2">{{cite news | last = McCarra | first = Kevin | title = World Cup 2010: Argentina exposed by Germany's perfect balance | newspaper = [[卫报|The Guardian]] | date = 2010-07-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190418130840/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/jul/04/world-cup-2010-argentina-germany | url = https://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/jul/04/world-cup-2010-argentina-germany | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2019-04-18}}</ref>。2014年6月6日，德国队在[[美因茨|美因茨]]举办的友谊赛上迎战[[亚美尼亚国家足球队|亚美尼亚队]]并以6比1大胜，克洛泽在他的第132场国际比赛中攻入第69球，打破[[盖德·穆勒|盖德·穆勒]]1966至1974年间在62场比赛踢进68球的纪录<ref name="armenia">{{cite news | title = Germany 6–1 Armenia | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2014-06-07 | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/27383453 | accessdate = 2020-07-25 | archivedate = 2019-04-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190424031734/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/27383453 | deadurl = no}}</ref>此后他又在[[2014年国际足协世界杯|2014年国际足协世界杯]]上踢进两球，以参加137场国际比赛并踢入71球的纪录退役。他攻入的最后一球是[[巴西对德国_(2014年国际足协世界杯)|以7比1大胜东道主巴西队的比赛]]，对此克洛泽以16枚入球超越罗纳尔多，成为国际足协世界杯史上最佳射手。<ref name="sixteen" />

除在世界杯正式比赛打进16球外，克洛斯还在资格赛踢入13球，[[欧洲足球锦标赛|欧洲足球锦标赛]]正式比赛破门三次，资格赛16次，剩下的进球中23个来自友谊赛。遭克洛斯破门次数最多的是奥地利队，共有六次，其次是[[阿塞拜疆国家足球队|阿塞拜疆队]]和[[瑞典国家足球队|瑞典队]]，均为五次。<ref name="eufoot" />

